# Personal data stays out of git by default. This repo is yours — if you WANT
# your contact data versioned locally, delete the data lines below. Never push
# with them removed unless the remote is private and yours.
# (Patterns use dir/* rather than dir/ so the .gitkeep negations work — git
# never descends into a fully-ignored directory.)
imports/*
!imports/.gitkeep
contacts/*
!contacts/.gitkeep
!contacts/normalized
contacts/normalized/*
!contacts/normalized/.gitkeep
!contacts/enrichments
contacts/enrichments/*
!contacts/enrichments/.gitkeep
# profile/ holds the owner's life history. Ignore the whole dir except the
# template — a second profile file (e.g. an era cheat-sheet split out of
# about-me) must not land trackable in the public tree.
profile/*
!profile/about-me.example.md

# Machinery
node_modules/
.env
*.log
.stop-enrichment
.enrich-lock

# local Claude Code settings + their backups (never publish)
.claude/settings.local.json*
